Cousin Brother/ Sister


Let's understand: The word cousin does not come with any rider word like brother or sister. In case you want to specify the gender of your cousin, you use the corresponding pronoun.

Incorrect Usages: I went to the party with my aunt and cousin sister.
                                My cousin brother lives in the US, he is so much fun.

Correct Usages: I went to the party with my aunt and cousin.
                             My cousin lives in the US, he is so much fun.
